": 2283, \"to\": 2307}, {\"ngram\": \"valuable data\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2356}, {\"ngram\": \"energy systems\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Strategically, it has enabled us to meet change agents, international decision-makers, industrialists, \\u2026 reinforcing a global network of sharing of knowledge and innovation.\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"change agents\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2430}, {\"ngram\": \"international decision-makers\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2461}, {\"ngram\": \"industrialists\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2477}, {\"ngram\": \"a global network\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2509}, {\"ngram\": \"sharing\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2520}, {\"ngram\": \"knowledge\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"innovation\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Victorien Erussard, founder and captain of Energy Observer: \\\"This stopover in Paris closes a chapter in an exceptional seven-year human and technological adventure.\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2594, \"end\": 2609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Energy_Observer\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Energy Observer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Energy_Observer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Energy_Observer\"}, {\"begin\": 2629, \"end\": 2634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4544526002159044e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Victorien Erussard\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2569}, {\"ngram\": \"founder\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2578}, {\"ngram\": \"captain\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2590}, {\"ngram\": \"This stopover\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2625}, {\"ngram\": \"a chapter\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2651}, {\"ngram\": \"an exceptional seven-year human and technological adventure\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the adventure does not end here.\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the adventure\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have matured, we have moved forward, and our mission is not over.\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our mission\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2808}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not giving up, and I am not waiting until 2050 to achieve carbon neutrality!\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"carbon neutrality\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The task is arduous and the obstacles numerous, but when I see what we have achieved in seven years, I am convinced we can do much more.\\\"\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 3041, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The task\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2912}, {\"ngram\": \"the obstacles\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2941}, {\"ngram\": \"seven years\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3003}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Paris, Energy Observer will continue to inspire and raise awareness among the public and public decision-makers, demonstrating that concrete, sustainable solutions exist and are implementable today.\", \"from\": 3043, \"to\": 3244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3046, \"end\": 3051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4544526002159044e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3053, \"end\": 3068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Energy_Observer\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Energy Observer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Energy_